                            <p style="margin-bottom: 0.2em">
                                UC Berkeley presented great opportunities to branch out and challenge myself in pursuit of my 
                                dreams. 
                                I was able to further pursue my interest in Computer Science by taking courses such as:
                            </p>
                            <ol>
                                <!--<li>CS 10 - The Beauty and Joy of Computing</li>-->
                                <li>CS 61A - Structure and Interpretation of Computer Programs</li>
                                <li>CS 61B - Data Structures</li>
