                        <img class="my-bg-pic vert-spaced" src="/images/ucsb.jpg">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 my-bg-text">
                        <h3 class="my-bg-title">University of California, Santa Barbara</h3>
                        <h4 class="my-bg-subtitle">Curriculum in Statistical Science, B.S.</h4>
                        <div class="my-bg-content">
                            <p style="margin-bottom: 0.2em">
                                The two years that I spent in UCSB as a Statistical Science major truly changed my life. UCSB was 
                                wonderful: as a student, one is able to work hard in the pursuit of one's goals and play hard when one 
                                needs a break. I will forever be grateful that UCSB generously invested its resources to nurture and 
                                grow my potential as a student by granting me a place in the UCSB Letters & Science Honors Program. 
                                Of all the courses I took in UCSB, three left the greatest, lasting impressions on me:
